    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Settlements in which almost all the habitations are confined to a defined area. The nucleus is usually surrounded by agricultural land.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
